<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Hildegard von Bingen (1098-1179)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text">Jumping back in time, and way back to <a href="/discover-music/humour/medieval-artist-horse-funny-fail/">medieval</a> times, lets meet <a href="/composers/bingen/">Hildegard von Bingen</a>. She was a saint, poet and composer who in her lifetime was one of the most influential women in Europe. </p><p class="paragraph-text">She wrote really expressive music that broke boundaries in her time. And she was a rare figure of the Middle Ages in leaving behind manuscripts of her songs  it meant that on around the 800th anniversary of her birth, the music community was able to rediscover her work and revive her songs.   </p><p class="paragraph-text"><strong>Read more: </strong><a href="/composers/bingen/guides/discovering-great-composers-hildegard-von-bingen/"><strong>Explore the life and music of great composer, Hildegard von Bingen</strong></a></p>
