<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Edward Elgar (18571934)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text">English composer <a href="/composers/elgar/">Edward Elgar</a> managed to capture whole landscapes, national moods and deep emotional complexity in his music, all at the same time. </p><p class="paragraph-text">Hes remembered and revered for the <em>Enigma Variations</em>, the Pomp and Circumstance Marches, his concertos for <a href="/discover-music/instruments/violin/">violin</a> and <a href="/discover-music/instruments/cello/">cello</a>, and two symphonies.</p>
