<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Giuseppe Verdi (18131901)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text"><a href="/composers/verdi/">Verdi</a>, for many, is quite simply the greatest Italian opera composer who ever lived. </p><p class="paragraph-text">He composed <em>La Traviata</em>, <em>Aida</em>, <em>Nabucco,</em> <em>Rigoletto</em>, <em>Otello</em> the list of best and most-performed operas goes on. And his arias, La donna  mobile and Si Un Jour remain favourites still today.  </p>
