</svg>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Richard Strauss (18641949)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text">Another Richard, this one <a href="/composers/strauss/">Strauss</a>  and not to be confused with the Johannes Strausses <a href="/composers/strauss-i/">I</a> and <a href="/composers/strauss-ii/">II</a>, who were pre-occupied with waltzes and light music  also made a mark with opera. </p><p class="paragraph-text">His one-act opera <em>Salome</em>, which premiered in 1905, shocked the classical music establishment with its erotic and murderous themes, set against a religious context, and got itself banned through censorship for a time. </p><p class="paragraph-text">His other big works include the orchestral works <em>Also Sprach Zarathustra</em> and <em>Don Quixote</em>.   </p>
<div class="video-container">
<div class="video-facade video-facade__brightcove" id="video_facade_brightcove_6065670326001" data-video-provider="brightcove" data-video-id="6065670326001" data-account="6057949401001">
