<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Antonin Dvok (1841-1904)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text"><a href="/composers/dvorak/">Antonn Dvok</a> was a Czech composer of dazzling late <a href="/discover-music/periods-genres/romantic/">Romantic</a> orchestral music. </p><p class="paragraph-text">A champion of folk idioms of Moravia and his native Bohemia, Dvok is celebrated for works like his Slavonic Dances, and his Symphony No. 9 From the New World.</p>
