</svg>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">Leonard Bernstein (1918-1990)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text"><a href="/discover-music/periods-genres/modern/20th-century-best-composers/">20th-century</a> American composer and conductor, <a href="/composers/bernstein-l/">Leonard Bernstein</a>, was as prolific at composing for the concert hall as he was for film and TV. </p><p class="paragraph-text"><em>West Side Story</em> and <em>Candide </em>electrified the stage, and his work in TV, bringing classical music to the masses through 53 televised <em>Young Peoples Concerts</em>, introduced an entire generation to classical music.  </p><p class="paragraph-text"><strong>Read more: </strong><a href="/composers/bernstein-l/"><strong>Bradley Coopers Bernstein biopic is officially coming to Netflix</strong></a></p>
<div class="video-container">
<div class="video-facade video-facade__brightcove" id="video_facade_brightcove_6222498993001" data-video-provider="brightcove" data-video-id="6222498993001" data-account="6057949401001">
<img src="https://cf-images.eu-west-1.prod.boltdns.net/v1/static/6057949401001/6e716d47-9e4f-4efc-aa17-15be630d766f/202d30d1-e5db-44dd-afb1-353e0d4c09e5/640x360/match/image.jpg" loading="lazy" />
<div class="title">
<p>Marin Alsop on her musical hero, Leonard Bernstein</p>
</div>
