</div>
</div>
</li>
<li class="collection__item">
<h2 class="title">John Williams (1932-present)</h2>
<p class="paragraph-text"><a href="/composers/williams/">John Williams</a> is an American film composer, responsible for writing the music that accompanies some of the worlds most beloved on-screen memories.</p><p class="paragraph-text">E.T. phoning home in the 1980s? Yep, Williams was with us. Dinosaurs stomping through a misjudged theme park in <em>Jurassic Park </em>in the 1990s? Williams again. </p><p class="paragraph-text">Broomsticks swerving and snitches flitting around the wizard <a href="/discover-music/periods-genres/film-tv/harry-potter-soundtrack-hedwig-theme-john-williams/">Harry Potter</a> in the 2000s? Again, were glad they called Williams. </p><p class="paragraph-text">A true legend and perfecter of the craft of 20th and 21st-century film music.   </p>
<div class="video-container">
<div class="video-facade video-facade__brightcove" id="video_facade_brightcove_6154000139001" data-video-provider="brightcove" data-video-id="6154000139001" data-account="6057949401001">
<img src="https://cf-images.eu-west-1.prod.boltdns.net/v1/jit/6057949401001/830a701e-0d9f-4b9c-a928-c30f7680a003/main/640x360/16s74ms/match/image.jpg" loading="lazy" />
